Event host and comedian, MC Fisayo Michael Olagunju aka MC Fish has reaffirmed undying love for his wife, actress Anita Joseph. The Emcee, who never misses an opportunity to express intense affection for his heartthrob, declared in a video that he’d always love her.   How ladies can actualise dreams- Omoni Oboli     Mr. P quits Zoom lottery platform     Why I exited Timaya’s record label, by King Perry   According to him, the love he has for his wife is enough for the both of them should she ever stopped loving him. Addressing his wife who stood with him near the poll side, MC Fish said: “I keep saying it, even if you don’t love me; I still love you. My love is enough for the both of us.”